BD volumes 1 and 2 of The World God Only Knows - Goddesses Arc, brought to you by Vivid.

Includes a second sub track with honorifics and Japanese titles (e.g. "Kami-nii-sama"). To switch tracks using the recommended CCCP setup, press the S key on your keyboard or right-click the green arrow icon in the system tray.

This is a 1080p BD release encoded in 10bit h264 with FLAC audio. If you have any problems with playback or subtitle rendering, please make sure you're using the latest version of the CCCP.
